        "detail": "evaluatePredicate case 'plan_produced' only checks 'plan.produced', but resolvePlanProduced in predicates.ts checks 'plan.produced' || 'plan.created' || 'artifact.plan'. The SM-003 comment at the top of state-machine.ts ('Predicate evaluation is heuristic — SM-003 will make it rigorous') acknowledges this. Until SM-003 lands, the state machine may fail to match events that predicates.ts would find."
